---

<BaseLayout pageTitle="Speakers Info" subtitle="We're very pleased to have you at DevFest Bari 2023! Here's some information you'll need to know:">
  <div class="grid grid-flow-row gap-4 mt-5 mb-7">
    <div class="pb-4">
