      <p>We are hosting an Opening Dinner on <span class="font-semibold">Friday, December 1st 2023, from 21:00</span>.
      <p>We'll let you know additional details about the dinner venue soon.</p>
      <p>Meanwhile, please RSVP in our <AnchorLink href="https://forms.gle/c3JmBYMc5qDuA5fG8" placeholder="Google Form" />.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="pb-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl pb-2 sm:truncate sm:text-3xl sm:tracking-tight">Communication üí¨</h2>
      <p>Join our <AnchorLink href={WebsiteConfig.TELEGRAM_SPEAKERS_GROUP} placeholder="Speakers Telegram group" />!</p>
    </div>
    <div class="pb-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl pb-2 sm:truncate sm:text-3xl sm:tracking-tight">Socials #Ô∏è‚É£</h2>
      <p>Announce to the world you're a Speaker of DevFest Bari 2023!</p>
      <p>We're publishing daily posts featuring speakers on our <AnchorLink href={WebsiteConfig.FACEBOOK_PAGE} placeholder="Facebook" /> and <AnchorLink href={WebsiteConfig.INSTAGRAM_PAGE} placeholder="Instagram" /> pages, please share them with your followers with the hashtag <span class="font-semibold">#DevFestBari23</span>!</p>
      <p class="py-4">There is also this <AnchorLink href="https://www.canva.com/design/DAFzafkLNi0/eD9xaI_wsvm9XZlZgAbA2Q/edit" placeholder="Canva template" /> that you can share.
      <p class="pt-4">You can use this copy:</p>
      <ClipboardCopyer />
